thread.title_full: Personalized Paper Manufacturing Group reviewed by Camareigh

author: Camareigh
title: Camareigh
text: Shortly after I submitted my order I received an e-mail from Deborah stating that my images were not of high enough resolution to be printed so I fixed the images that needed to be fixed and sent it off again and she got it sent off to production quickly. We received our notepads quickly and they all look amazing!
